metadata.name: LATENT DREAMS // NFTNYC23
metadata.description:
LATENT DREAMS is a collection of works by 21 artists that exhibited works depicting experiences, memories, ideas, from or revolving around Dreams. This exhibition was live on April 13th at The NFT Gallery during NFTNYC week, 2023.

Hosted by Joyn + Curated by BLAC.ai

A permanent gallery of the works is on display here:  
https://app.joyn.xyz/gallery/latent-dreams-f47aea8bdcbd
